---
title: Smart Korean-Inspired Turkey Salad with Creamy Sesame Dressing
description: This bountiful salad is bursting with colour, Korean-inspired flavours and wholesome veggies! Spicy soy turkey and a creamy, gochujang-based dressing round out the plate for a delicious, light way to start your week!

